<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="set-off">set off</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>出发；动身：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We ought to set off at 7:00, while the roads are empty.
我们应该7点出发，趁那时路上没什么车。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>触响（警报）；放（烟火）：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Some boys are setting off fireworks in the street.
一些男孩正在街上放烟火。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>引发；激发：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His rude reply set off a bad feeling of me.
他无礼的答复引起了我的反感。</p></div></div>